sentences.sContent: Over time, developers subdivided the land.
sentences.sCn: 开发商们渐渐地把这块土地进行了再分割。

sentences.sContent: The house was subdivided into apartments.
sentences.sCn: 房子又被分割成几个套间。

words.tran: 细分；分部；供出卖而分成的小块土地

trans.tranOther: to divide into smaller parts something that is already divided
